content.text: The geometric structure (𝔾Ø) represents a space of cognitive layers, and the arithmetic of the system (𝔸Ø) defines algebraic operations that emphasize the special role of Ø, a singularity absorbing values and obstructing standard algebraic properties such as commutativity and inverses
